Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.78,0:00:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,还真是壮观啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.00,0:00:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 很漂亮的首都
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.33,0:00:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,可是 好像没什么生气
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.84,0:00:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,本来想让你们看看我们繁荣的公国
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.60,0:00:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,但是现在没时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.87,0:00:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,先去找我父王
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.64,0:02:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,比兹 救援呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.51,0:02:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 难道你也发病了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.44,0:02:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,父王
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.44,0:02:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,什么 你们愿意帮助我们国家和国民吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.56,0:02:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.53,0:02:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,人数这么多
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.67,0:02:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,希娅 开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.20,0:02:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,坏劫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.87,0:03:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,泛块浪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.13,0:03:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,居然会有这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.82,0:03:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,应该够用一段时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.96,0:03:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,有机会妾身也想试一试
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.93,0:03:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,缪也要
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.51,0:03:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 接下来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.53,0:03:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,始？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.78,0:03:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,没事 刚刚魔眼石好像有点反应
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.40,0:03:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,领主
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.73,0:03:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,污染调查进度怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.80,0:03:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,绿洲和流出的河川水质调查
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.58,0:04:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,以及地下水的调查已经结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.89,0:04:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不过绿洲水底还没来得及调查
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.38,0:04:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,绿洲底下埋着什么古器物吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.38,0:04:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,警备和管理有用到某种古器物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.24,0:04:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,但是设在地面上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.47,0:04:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,所以那又是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.71,0:04:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,您干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.96,0:04:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,还挺灵巧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.71,0:04:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,始阁下 您这是在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.44,0:04:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,真顽固 那就再来50个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.56,0:04:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,休想
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.36,0:05:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.71,0:05:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,那魔物究竟是什么 是巴丘拉姆吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.36,0:05:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,无所谓 反正污染的源头应该就是它吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.64,0:05:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,多半是带着释放毒素的固有魔法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.20,0:05:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,这么说的确合情合理
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.73,0:05:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,但是你们能打败它吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.29,0:05:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.04,0:05:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,结束了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.47,0:05:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,绿洲里已经没有魔力反应了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.09,0:06:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不过不知道排除了污染源算不算净化成功
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.36,0:06:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.56,0:06:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,还是有污染
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.71,0:06:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,别这么泄气
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.42,0:06:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,新鲜的水源会不断冒出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.49,0:06:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,用不了多久绿洲就会恢复如初了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.09,0:06:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 缇奥说的没错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.62,0:06:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,可是 那个魔物究竟是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.13,0:06:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,是新的魔物沿着地下水游进来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.96,0:06:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,可能是魔人族搞的鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.53,0:06:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,魔人族？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.40,0:06:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,既然阁下这么说 想必是有什么线索吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.09,0:06:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.00,0:06:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我们也自主进行了调查
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.38,0:06:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,但没想到有人能驱使如此魔物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.40,0:06:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,是我们太无知了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.76,0:06:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我代表国家和国民向你们表示感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.51,0:06:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你们拯救了这个国家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.49,0:06:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,好好感谢我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.44,0:06:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,绝对不能忘了我这份大恩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.09,0:07:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.78,0:07:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,噢~
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.91,0:07:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,各位听着
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.09,0:07:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,始
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.07,0:07:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,始大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.36,0:07:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,绿洲的污染源已经排除了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.42,0:07:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然还需要一些时间
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.44,0:07:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,但我们的绿洲很快就会恢复了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.58,0:07:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,而且 水的储量也有了保证
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.11,0:07:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,足够我们等到救援到来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.24,0:07:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,另外 这边几位金级冒险家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.89,0:07:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,接受了去古卢恩大火山采集静因石的委托
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.69,0:07:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,最后几天 大家振奋精神
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.76,0:07:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,一起打破这困境吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.27,0:07:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我留下来治疗患者们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.51,0:07:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,静因石就拜托你们了 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.78,0:07:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,反正也是顺路
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.87,0:07:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我会好好照看缪的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.40,0:07:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.56,0:08:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.18,0:08:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我会加油的 你们一定要平安回来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.49,0:08:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我等你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.11,0:08:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.07,0:08:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,要像刚刚和月姐姐亲亲一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.38,0:08:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,和香织姐姐亲亲吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.89,0:08:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,亲了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.44,0:08:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,原来你看见了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.53,0:08:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,缪也想和爸爸亲亲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.98,0:08:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,等缪长大一点再来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.69,0:08:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,这是怎么一回事 回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.78,0:08:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,大家是去干活的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.31,0:08:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么你会和月亲嘴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.16,0:08:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么会这样 有这必要吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.89,0:08:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,很开心是吗 把我给忘了是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.82,0:08:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,美味无比
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.51,0:08:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,缪 我们走了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.78,0:08:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,留在这里乖乖听话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.82,0:09:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,好的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.80,0:09:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,热死了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.96,0:09:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,要变成烤兔子了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.49,0:09:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,妾身倒是觉得刚刚好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.51,0:09:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,不能被热得发痒 真是可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.33,0:09:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,待会儿把你扔岩浆里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.07,0:10:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,这里就是入口吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.87,0:10:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我们走
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.98,0:10:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.87,0:10:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.89,0:10:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.73,0:10:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,这里怎么搞的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.98,0:10:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是静因石吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.02,0:10:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 没错 主人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.89,0:10:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,好小
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.49,0:10:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,都是些小石子儿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.33,0:10:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,已经被采得差不多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.36,0:10:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,想要大丰收
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.22,0:10:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,得深入到人迹罕至的地方才行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.40,0:11:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,再往前似乎就没人能活着回来了 别大意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.24,0:11:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,绝祸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.07,0:11:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,来玩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.96,0:11:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,始大人 让我来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.42,0:11:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 你想试试那个是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.82,0:11:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.16,0:11:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.78,0:12:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,始大人 这个新功能威力大得吓人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.91,0:12:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,貌似是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.38,0:12:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,魔力冲击变换
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.38,0:12:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,还以为不怎么样 没想到还挺强
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.04,0:12:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,这可不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.09,0:12:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.47,0:12:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,居然还有这样的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.87,0:12:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,有了这么多静因石
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.82,0:12:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,安卡吉的人们就能得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.58,0:12:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 接下来只要攻略这个大迷宫就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.89,0:12:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,热死了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.51,0:12:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,希娅 心静自然凉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.89,0:12:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,那些流动的都是水
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.69,0:12:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你看 好凉快
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.20,0:13:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,主人 月快坏掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.84,0:13:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你倒是挺精神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.47,0:13:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.27,0:13:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,月 弄点冰出来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.62,0:13:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,脑袋快热炸了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.00,0:13:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.44,0:13:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,真凉快 活过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.91,0:13:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,呜喵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.84,0:13:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,放松之余 记得把汗擦擦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.36,0:13:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,着凉了反应会变迟钝的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.29,0:13:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.33,0:13:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,主人看起来还很轻松啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.82,0:13:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,比不上你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.69,0:13:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,这温度确实很热
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.09,0:13:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,事先准备点冷冻系的古器物就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.53,0:13:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,连主人都束手无策了就说明
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.20,0:14:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,恐怕这就是这大迷宫的主题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.71,0:14:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,主题？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.91,0:14:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.98,0:14:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,大迷宫是用来挑战神的试炼对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.62,0:14:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,那每个大迷宫应该都有各自的主题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.02,0:14:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,比如奥尔库斯大迷宫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.69,0:14:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,是与众多魔物 展开各式各样的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.96,0:14:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,不断积累经验
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.84,0:14:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,莱森大迷宫则是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.49,0:14:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,脱离魔力这种强大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.24,0:14:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,锻炼应对各种攻击的反应能力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.29,0:14:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,而这个古卢恩大火山
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.20,0:14:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,是要克服酷热对集中注意力的阻碍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.60,0:14:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,在此条件之上锻炼应对突袭的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.22,0:14:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,大概是这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.31,0:14:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.82,0:14:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,之前没仔细想过
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.09,0:14:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,试炼本身 就是解放者们的教导吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.73,0:15:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,始帮我擦干净
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.73,0:15:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,好像有类似的游乐项目
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.49,0:15:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,始大人 又是隧道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.93,0:15:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,差不多应该到山脚的高度了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.00,0:15:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,说不定会出现什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.82,0:15:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.84,0:15:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,抓紧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.80,0:15:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,来翔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.82,0:16:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,看起来像埋着宝石
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.49,0:16:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,算上看不见的部分 差不多有百来个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.07,0:16:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,那里就是解放者的藏身之所吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.51,0:16:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,按照深度来看应该没错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.11,0:16:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,但这样一来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.20,0:16:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,应该会有最后的守护者 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.44,0:16:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我们渡过岩浆而来 感觉就像抄了近路
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.22,0:16:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,不能认为我们已经通过试炼了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.67,0:16:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.62,0:16:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,绝祸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.60,0:17:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,月 我去看看那个岛 掩护我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.89,0:17:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.40,0:17:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,是魔石吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.49,0:17:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,还要来多少条啊 烦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.38,0:17:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,始 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.84,0:17:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 没事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.49,0:17:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,看来是动真格的了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.98,0:17:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,果然那个岛就是终点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.96,0:17:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,简直就是在说 要想过此路 先打倒我们再说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.56,0:17:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,可是 刚刚它们很轻松就再生了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.67,0:17:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,真的有机会打败它们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.53,0:18:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,恐怕和我们在安卡吉对付的巴丘拉姆魔物一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.64,0:18:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 身体里应该有生成岩浆的核心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.04,0:18:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是魔石在里面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.60,0:18:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,岩浆妨碍我的魔眼确定精准位置了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.51,0:18:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不过只能破坏掉那东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.60,0:18:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,这次可不是普通的子弹了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.13,0:18:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,休想得逞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.40,0:18:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,原来如此 像这样打倒它们就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.60,0:18:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.53,0:18:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,那我们也开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.60,0:18:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,黑玉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.18,0:18:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,乌拉哒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.60,0:19:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,这到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.42,0:19:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,魔石的确被击碎了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.31,0:19:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,难道通关条件不是打败那十条蛇吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.60,0:19:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,始大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.89,0:19:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,那边的宝石是不是碎掉了一些
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.78,0:19:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,现在击碎的宝石就有十一个了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.93,0:19:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,和我们一起打败的蛇数量一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.42,0:19:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.76,0:20:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,按照宝石的数量击败等量的蛇
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.42,0:20:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是说 打倒100条就是通关条件了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.60,0:20:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,这么热的条件下对付100条
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.84,0:20:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,也很切合迷宫的主题
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.38,0:20:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,既然这样 要做的事情就很简单了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.98,0:20:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,久违的一击了 好好品尝一番吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.20,0:20:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,现在是我领先一步了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.73,0:20:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,主人 要是妾身打倒的数量最多
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.93,0:20:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,请务必给予妾身奖励
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.02,0:20:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,光是缇奥大姐可不公平
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.16,0:20:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我也要参战
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.07,0:20:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,她们两个自顾自说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.64,0:20:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,那我也要两人世界约会一整天
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.40,0:20:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,雷龙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.40,0:21:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,月大人是最强的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.98,0:21:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,月是个BUG 绝对不正常
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.42,0:21:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,数量没增加了 看来这5条就是最后的了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.04,0:21:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.51,0:21:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,两条交给妾身吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.18,0:21:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,古卢恩大火山攻略完成
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.58,0:21:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.16,0:21:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,始
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.98,0:23:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,下集 黑与白
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.16,0:00:59.71,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}Tears streaming down your sorrow face
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.87,0:01:05.71,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}Came a long and painful road, you gave yourself away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.55,0:01:11.05,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}You saw everything, heaven to hell
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.34,0:01:17.47,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}You say you need a self redemption, to mend the broken wings
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.97,0:01:22.89,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}Drowning in the dark, no place to be
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.60,0:01:26.65,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}But I am by your side
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.94,0:01:28.48,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}You’re not alone
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.73,0:01:34.41,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}Daylight, shed a light so you won’t disappear
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.61,0:01:40.37,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}Cause I know where you belong, save your saddened heart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.37,0:01:46.08,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}With a flashback, screaming out but still we’re holding on
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.25,0:01:51.51,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}Waiting for the break of dawn for a new day to begin
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.97,0:01:54.76,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}Daylight, daylight
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.34,0:02:00.10,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}Stay a little while longer
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.40,0:22:12.73,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}全部　期待してみて幻だった
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.73,0:22:17.22,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}信じたかった　縋りたかった
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.13,0:22:23.93,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}身体の底に開いた螺旋状の穴
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.24,0:22:29.13,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}ボクだけじゃなく　キミにもなんだね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.58,0:22:38.29,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}許されることなど　もう望んじゃいない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.29,0:22:42.82,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}抱き寄せてもまた　わからないシルエット
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.82,0:22:47.40,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}躊躇いもなく傷つけた代償か
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.62,0:22:52.51,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}キミの側は　揺れてボクを離れた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.51,0:22:57.49,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}どちらが欲しいかなんて　残酷な問い神様は
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.49,0:23:02.07,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}何度ボクらに投げかける
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.07,0:23:07.09,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}道を違える度に　ボクの後ろに穴が開く
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.09,0:23:10.11,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}伸びた一本の影
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.42,0:23:16.58,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}誰もが手にし得る　小さな欠片で
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.82,0:23:21.18,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}何ができる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.18,0:23:26.33,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}どちらが欲しいかなんて　残酷な問い神様は
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.33,0:23:31.18,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}何度ボクらに投げかける
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.40,0:22:12.73,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}期待的一切皆为虚空一场
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.73,0:22:17.22,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}破灭的希望　虚伪的幻想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.13,0:22:23.93,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嵌入身体的伤口深不见底
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.24,0:22:29.13,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不仅是我　你也背负同样的伤
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.58,0:22:38.29,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}早已不再奢望　求得谁人原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.29,0:22:42.82,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哪怕怀中相拥　徒留轮廓难辨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.82,0:22:47.40,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}甘愿承伤不曾犹豫的代价
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.62,0:22:52.51,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我步履蹒跚　忍痛离开你身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.51,0:22:57.49,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}神明凛然在上　抛下两难抉择
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.49,0:23:02.07,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不断拷问你我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.07,0:23:07.09,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}几步对错　令我身负百孔千疮
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.09,0:23:10.11,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}形单影只渐行渐远
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.42,0:23:16.58,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}希望碎片　谁人不曾拥有
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.82,0:23:21.18,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}又能作何挣扎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.18,0:23:26.33,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}神明凛然在上　抛下两难抉择
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.33,0:23:31.18,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不断拷问你我
